descriptionHtml:
Whitefield Cottage

[Author(s)]
Margolotta, distributed via joajo927

[Version]
1.01

[Description]
Whitefield Cottage is a medium sized home near Whiterun stables. It contains all the necessary crafting equipment while still being snug and cozy. It is available from the start; you have a map marker to guide you to it. All containers are safe for storage.

Bedroom:
	Bed
	2 Bookshelves
	4 containers
	A few harvestable plants

Kitchen area:
	Cooking pot
	11 containers

Smithy:
	Forge
	Grindstone
	Smelter
	Tanning rack
	Workbench
	5 containers

Enchanting/alchemy area:
	Alchemy Lab
	Arcane Enchanter
	2 display rack for weapons and shields
	2 display cases for daggers
	9 containers
	A few harvestable plants

Outside:
	Chopping block and axe
	1 container

[Change Log]
1.01 Estetic changes an a minor bug fix

1.0 Initial release

[Installation]
Use NMM. Or, if you\'re into that sort of thing, extract the files into your skyrim\\data folder, open your mod manager of choise, and check PlayerHomeWhitefieldCottage.esp.

[Uninstallation]
Use NMM or delete PlayerHomeWhitefieldCottage.esp from your skyrim\\data folder.

[Incompatabilities]
May conflict with any mod that alters the area between Whiterun Stable and Western Watchtower

[Compatabilities]
Should be compatible with anything that doesn\'t alter the cells it occupies.

[Thanks to]
Eldiabs, for his Modders Resource-Weapon Racks-Bookshelves-Plaques-Mannequins

[Tools Used]
Creation Kit
TES5Edit
Readme Generator by DarkSaber2328

[Permissions]
Feel free to use this mod any way you like, as long as you give us credit.
